OL,3,CFormer bride returns to stage with
OL,4,Clost wedding ring Christmas surprise
OL,6,FFollowing their conversation, Lucy
OL,7,Fcontacted the jeweller that had made
OL,8,Ftheir original bands to get one made
OL,9,Ffor Ben, which was delivered as a very
OL,10,Fspecial Christmas gift.
OL,12,FLucy and Ben's wedding in 2006 made it
OL,13,Fonto the front page of their local
OL,14,Fnewspaper after Lucy woke up that day
OL,15,Fwith food poisoning and spent the
OL,16,Fmorning in hospital - but made it to
OL,17,Fthe theatre, just in time, to tie the
