OL,4,Clost wedding ring Christmas surprise
OL,6,FLucy said: "After Ben lost his wedding
OL,7,Fring we searched, but the fine sand of
OL,8,Fthe Dutch dunes made it impossible to
OL,9,Ffind.
OL,11,F"Ben never got a new ring made, but a
OL,12,Ffew weeks ago out of the blue, he
OL,13,Fsuddenly said that he would like to
OL,14,Fhave a new wedding ring.
OL,16,F"So, I went back to our jeweller who
OL,17,Fmade our rings, to commission a new
OL,18,Fring for Ben.
