OL,3,CFormer bride returns to stage with
OL,4,Clost wedding ring Christmas surprise
OL,6,F"It feels very special, and I thought
OL,7,Fit was a lovely and fun thing to do,
OL,8,Fespecially as it is Christmas.
OL,10,F"Theatre Royal Winchester is very
OL,11,Fclose to our hearts ` we love seeing
OL,12,Fshows here ` so I am thrilled they've
OL,13,Fallowed us to use the stage once more
OL,14,Ffor this special moment."
OL,16,FFollowing the presentation, Ben said
OL,17,Fto Lucy: "Apart from giving us our
OL,18,Fchildren, this was the most amazing
OL,19,Fthing you have ever done for me."
